latestPosts.caption:
I seek for kindness, compassion & warmth in people & you my jaan are all of that & more. How lucky am I? 
Happiest Birthday!! 
To the funniest man in the room, 
You’re that one friend that everyone wants in their lives. 
I am so proud of all that you do baby. 
I appreciate you, every single day, my gift of joy. 
Live has never felt more complete. 
I love you baby, so much more than all the times I say, I love you. I love you. I love you. 😁💕🫂

When you are engaged to a man that doesn’t like taking photos, well, you rebel (photo 4) and then you succumb (photo 5) and laugh about it. 

Also also, how handsome is my fiancé?! 😍♥️
